column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  s.specobjid, s.specClass, s.z FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND g BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.z BETWEEN # and #  AND g-i BETWEEN # and #  AND p.petroR5#_r BETWEEN # and #
